Class FinancialService

java.lang.Object
hu.nye.service.FinancialService
All Implemented Interfaces:
FinancialServiceInterface
public class FinancialService extends Object implements FinancialServiceInterface
Service class for handling financial operations. This class provides methods to generate invoices, track expenses, and generate financial reports.
